"""
Essentia Music Tagger
Analyze audio files with Essentia ML models and write genre/mood tags.
Stripped-down standalone version for WBs-Beautiful-TUI-Filemanager.
Based on: https://github.com/WB2024/Essentia-to-Metadata
"""

